{"tid":2286729,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"達明一派唱盡社會荒誕  黃耀明三度落淚 望世界不要變得更壞","createTime":"2020-11-15T08:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T08:30:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"83cc81b6b55aee18aad54c679961ec2b8ca35bdf","tid":2286729,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T08:30:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201115/GSGHGGWDBBDVRGFCB77UYZRCHE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201115%2FGSGHGGWDBBDVRGFCB77UYZRCHE%2F&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BB4w7aMtX%2B%2FJ%2BUdoe8qorTI%3D&h=3576da85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201115%2FGSGHGGWDBBDVRGFCB77UYZRCHE%2F&h=54c94af7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201115/GSGHGGWDBBDVRGFCB77UYZRCHE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n達明一派唱盡社會荒誕 <br />\n黃耀明三度落淚 望世界不要變得更壞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/89TrZTFhWx90yMA1qP_g8qnQ7Gk=/640x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GLDSZBP6URB53OWP2NJSOOOYWQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F89TrZTFhWx90yMA1qP_g8qnQ7Gk%3D%2F640x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGLDSZBP6URB53OWP2NJSOOOYWQ.jpg&h=6f1d94b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■達明一派前晚在灣仔舉行演唱會頭場，兩人穿上以膠片做成如「連儂牆」的白西裝獻唱。<br />\n<br />\n達明一派前晚在灣仔新伊館舉行首場「REPLAY LIVE演唱會」，一向敢言的黃耀明，透過演繹早在1989年六四事件前後推出的《意難平》及《神經》大碟內的歌曲，表達現今社會不公及政治荒誕的實況，。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：不忘為平權發聲<br />\n<br />\n黃耀明及劉以達組成的達明一派前晚開騷，全場爆滿。開場不久，明哥唱《情流夜中環》落淚，。。。。。。。。。。。。。，接着明哥指向台下睇騷的何韻詩說：「睇佢爛身爛勢，但內心非常強大。」阿詩聞言站起來向大家揮手。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/x8254KoL-cawhh1sHCghCfZUp2Y=/640x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UXOBO6D7RZG3BBCMSBOI5PJ4VE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fx8254KoL-cawhh1sHCghCfZUp2Y%3D%2F640x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUXOBO6D7RZG3BBCMSBOI5PJ4VE.jpg&h=1567a020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■明哥見劉以達（右）以長髮配辮仔造型出場，笑指拍檔去錯地方。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/J3hVl0A61WfOwp3hKH4Z3rEmKd0=/640x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FVDYSTD2ZRFWZC2BELY3V4ZSZU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJ3hVl0A61WfOwp3hKH4Z3rEmKd0%3D%2F640x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFVDYSTD2ZRFWZC2BELY3V4ZSZU.jpg&h=81691a3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■劉以達唱《排名不分先後左右忠奸》時，身旁的幕牆出現政界人士的名字。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2xaE6wHcYGVoc5Suew8AmELGSYA=/640x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TN5NAVPHIRF4XJHXM2CTMCYEJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2xaE6wHcYGVoc5Suew8AmELGSYA%3D%2F640x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTN5NAVPHIRF4XJHXM2CTMCYEJM.jpg&h=58bf30a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■因應疫情符合法例規定下，達明一派演唱會全場只能有75%觀眾入座。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歌衫似「連儂牆」<br />\n<br />\n當達明唱出《四季交易會》時，他們回想當年錄碟後是1989年5月，在新聞中看到天安門上學生聚集及靜坐，第一個反應是：「呢個地方有機會，但之後越來越危險。」唱畢明哥再說：「估唔到呢首歌仍然有感覺，睇返我哋立法會，係咪好似交易會？」接着明哥及劉以達換上以一塊塊膠片做成、看似是「連儂牆」的白衫西裝出場演唱《諸神的黃昏》。<br />\n<br />\n及後唱完《天問》，明哥表示日前填詞人周耀輝曾在fb出了關於《天問》的post，又謂最少在這幾個晚上可不可問上天的問題：「唔可以停、質問不公平嘅事，喺咁嘅社會氣氛下，呢啲歌可以唱幾耐，今日佢哋可以話立法會議會議員唔愛國，將來香港人唔知使唔使審查愛唔愛國？以下呢首歌我哋有諗過cut唔cut，唱完會否俾人拉？我哋唔好怕，怕就輸一世，一路一路退後，習慣咗呢個方式、有乜就唱！」觀眾歡呼拍手，之後劉以達便唱出歌詞內有內地及香港政界人名的《排名不分先後左右忠奸》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qrvWC6Mpe1xAN_0v0MMXT8Vu_Mo=/640x481/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JC7KYWMX55CRDDLUDH2GWELDMU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqrvWC6Mpe1xAN_0v0MMXT8Vu_Mo%3D%2F640x481%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJC7KYWMX55CRDDLUDH2GWELDMU.jpg&h=90f75813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■明哥提到自己印象中沒有唱過《情流夜中環》，不禁落淚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eax40JptEJJg1sYywQODK11UT9Q=/640x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3OWNA3GXKJAAZJISIDTP4VKKIQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Feax40JptEJJg1sYywQODK11UT9Q%3D%2F640x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3OWNA3GXKJAAZJISIDTP4VKKIQ.jpg&h=614503a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■明哥唱到《愛彌留》副歌時兩度淚灑舞台。<br />\n<br />\n明哥表示《你情我願》一曲原裝版本內有混入英國國歌，他笑說：「如果加中國國歌，大家可能俾人拉。」此時有觀眾笑，明哥即提醒：「你哋笑都可能俾人拉！1990年英國考慮畀居英權我哋，但𠵱家先畀，歌背後係話好諷刺，養母唔理我哋，生母唔知想點對我哋。大家𠵱家有啲想走；有啲又走唔到，我哋可以唔使走，因為呢個係我哋地方，但生母當我哋係殖民，好悲涼。」明哥唱到《愛彌留》前提到副歌歌詞是要將夢想變成行動，唱到該部份時他再落淚，觀眾大叫：「我哋支持你。」之後明哥唱到副歌他再次落淚，更一度要擰轉身抹眼淚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CyRaSEvFis7cBgf6wmq6l4NuGyo=/640x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XH3G2GB5BZF5LFYWUNKRD3RB5I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCyRaSEvFis7cBgf6wmq6l4NuGyo%3D%2F640x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXH3G2GB5BZF5LFYWUNKRD3RB5I.jpg&h=76961b83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■坐在台下睇騷的何韻詩，被明哥讚內心非常強大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/d1i8AgCh04tT7wgeBa2AJoJa1kk=/640x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6AZ4226IT5GO5KJHAV2KNGR6VA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fd1i8AgCh04tT7wgeBa2AJoJa1kk%3D%2F640x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6AZ4226IT5GO5KJHAV2KNGR6VA.jpg&h=51302862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■戴上口罩的林海峰到場欣賞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mbJPB7O4dJqK2Wq1Zu7NFA5S_QI=/640x854/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QHQGN7POVJCMLMXFYFOBK7TGRA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmbJPB7O4dJqK2Wq1Zu7NFA5S_QI%3D%2F640x854%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQHQGN7POVJCMLMXFYFOBK7TGRA.jpg&h=da1e9737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■明哥介紹樂隊成員時，被對方親暱錫面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新歌寫給戰友<br />\n<br />\nEncore時觀眾亮起手機燈再大叫：「香港人加油！」兩人唱《恐怖分子》前，明哥直指現在世界荒謬，希望大家要努力令它不要變得更壞，他說：「我好掛住上面嘅朋友，我好愛國，你唔好冤枉我，愛國先會寫呢啲、唱呢啲歌，民建聯嘅人會唔會唱呢啲歌？」之後明哥唱出寫給全世界的戰友及手足的新歌《今天世上所有地方》，最後介紹樂隊成員後圓滿結束。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fHPfrSMtbauV_ac8_qPp2rW0FxA=/397x1154/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QZALDAUWFZDVRALTN6XIXMHS5Y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfHPfrSMtbauV_ac8_qPp2rW0FxA%3D%2F397x1154%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQZALDAUWFZDVRALTN6XIXMHS5Y.gif&h=41afdb44&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}